verbose_text: To perturb Hemogen function in zebrafish, we first injected wild-type zebrafish embryos at the one-cell stage with an antisense morpholino oligonucleotide (MO), Hem-1, targeted to the translation start codon of the Hemogen transcript (Hem1).
